{"task_id":"TASK-030","finding_type":"context_loss","content":"User expressed critical frustration: 'Nao saia fazendo coisas AD-HOC, utilize o Metodo!!!' - AI was doing ad-hoc work instead of following BMAD methodology properly.","source_line":488}
